The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | Ballesteros operation
                                                                                                                                                                                                     Ballesteros operation
                      
	Madrid: Five-time major winner Seve Ballesteros will undergo another operation on Friday to ease swelling to his brain, the Madrid hospital treating him said on Thursday. The patient Mr Severiano Ballesteros remains stable within the seriousness (of his condition), Hospital La Paz in Madrid said in a statement.         
	Doctors operated on Ballesteros to remove a brain tumour on October 14. (Reuters)                                                                                                                          
